short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: DATEX developer tools integrated in the browser developer console

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Debug your UIX and DATEX web apps with the DATEX developer tools integrated into the Chrome DevTools.

The DATEX DevTools extension adds a DATEX panel to the DevTool, which includes DATEX Workbench inspection tools.
